text: Sigrid Jacobsen (born 26 April 1990) is a Faroese footballer who plays as a midfielder for Klaksvíkar Ítróttarfelag. She has been a member of the Faroe Islands women's national team. ==References== Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Faroese women's footballers Category:Faroe Islands women's international footballers
